    "description": "In <u>BomboCat</u> play as Guerrilla: a mouse artilleryman whose cannon is capable of destroying the fortresses of his jams enemies. However, be careful not to damage your allies, calculating each shot as best you can. Complete challenges to earn stars that will allow you to unlock devastating new abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136140/extras/50d0a81eb4eac783fccd91b4e5286e57.avif?t=1725898095\" width=346 height=166 /></span><br><br>Choose the right ammo to shoot between ice, wood and stone: you can shoot as many balls as you want, but pay attention on how much energy the cannon consumes with each shot.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136140/extras/376b4deff636dc2b61fa5e85efcf6043.poster.avif?t=1725898095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136140/extras/376b4deff636dc2b61fa5e85efcf6043.webm?t=1725898095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136140/extras/376b4deff636dc2b61fa5e85efcf6043.mp4?t=1725898095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136140/extras/5f7725996c54b9ddd3f537a836394854.avif?t=1725898095\" width=346 height=170 /></span><br><br>Across 3 different worlds tackle 30 hand-crafted levels that will offer a real challenge to players. Play aiming for jams or try to destroy buildings as best you can, starting from the bottom.<br><br>Save all the kidnapped Toms and put an end to the cats' kingdom!",
